fields.description:
h5.Description

jira ticket for - https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/issues/13053

When building to a device or dist-adhoc target on an M1 mac the build errors

h5.Steps to reproduce

1. Build to {{dist-adhoc}} or {{device}} on an M1 mac

h5.Actual

note: Build preparation complete
[TRACE] error: Provisioning profile "MyApp" doesn't include the currently selected device "iMac of me" (identifier ZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZZ). (in target 'MyApp' from project 'MyApp')


h5.Expected

No error
fields.summary: iOS: device or dist-adhoc builds on an M1 mac errors out
